name: Le Maestro Film Call Sheet
description:
50% of proceeds will be donated to thewereachfoundation.org for Haiti's earthquake victims.

The daily call sheet is a filmmaking term for the schedule crafted by the assistant director, using the director's shot list. It is issued to the cast and crew of a film production to inform them of where and when they should report for a particular day of filming. 

Storyline

 "Lifestyle of the new age low key investor" is a short film of my relentless career journey in music business, technology, investing and marketing. As I look back at the past 20 years. I've consistently took advantage of being able to wake up "One More Time" in good health and grab life by it's horns by the grace of God. Speeding up to the present time distributed ledger technology as lead me to take control of all of my musical creations. In this film I give credit to YouTube content creators (pioneers) who's helping me and thousands of people shape a brighter future. Cameo shot by some of Miami's self employed and small business owners make appearances and product placement.

Executive and music producer J.Classic-Maestro
Creative Director Maicol Diaz
